cdata.name: SMNX
cdata.desc:
The Solomon exchange is a user-friendly application where users canbuyi and sell cryptocurrenciesthrough their bank accounts and more. TheSolomon Exchange is backed by strong algorithmic mechanism to give users a choice among best cryptocurrency exchanges in the world.

The Solomon Exchange token is an Ethereum-based asset used to pay fees on the Solomon Exchange Local platform. These tokens arealso be used to distribute dividends to token holders.
